<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Charlize Theron grew up on a farm outside Benoni, South Africa, as the only child. She got an education as a ballet dancer and has danced both the "Swan Lake" and "The Nutcracker". There wasn't much for a young actress or dancer to do in South Africa, so she soon traveled to Europe and United States of America, where she got job at the Joffrey ...            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0000234/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm" >See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
