    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-personal-quote" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Personal Quote:</h4>
[on the media's reaction to her appearance in <a href="/title/tt0478134/?ref_=nm_dyk_qt1">In the Valley of Elah</a> (2007) It just bummed me out because I was, "What do you want? Do you want me to play a detective from Albuquerque who's a single mom in a Dior dress?" The way they focused on my appearance, I felt like it hurt [the film] and I was embarrassed because [director] <a href="/name/nm0353673/?ref_=nm_dyk_qt2">Paul Haggis</a> had worked really hard, and just because I had a ponytail...                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0000234/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_qt_sm#quotes" >See more</a> 
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
            <hr/>
        <div id="dyk-trivia" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Trivia:</h4>
Returned to work 4 months after adopting her son Jackson in order to begin filming <a href="/title/tt1392190/?ref_=nm_dyk_trv1">Mad Max: Fury Road</a> (2015).                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0000234/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_trv_sm#trivia" >See more</a>
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
    
